name: CABRONES
description: What happens when make a word zipper between CAR and BONES? Why CABRONES of course! What the heck does cabrones mean? Cabron in Spanish it has a few different meanings: (1. a male goat  2. slang for bastard  3. slang for dude  4. slang for someone who is badass  5. slang for damn it  6. someone who their wife is cheating on them). In this work we can assign the definition of damn it as we are crashing the words CAR and BONES together. What happens when we crash these words? ¡CABRONES!
